{
  "stem": "19969.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes this was a retired inspector general from the army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was a long-time friend.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Spent a lot of time, days and days, trying to research all the records pertaining to Dachau.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is probably the most complete document on existence relating to all peripheral things the days before, the days after what happened.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "These include army orders, corps orders, 42nd Division orders, 45th Division orders, all battalions journals.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything that could possibly relate to Dachau, he dug up.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the important thing that he dug up was the inspector general's report of the investigation and the subsequent action by the commanding general of the 7th United States Army and the 3rd United States Army.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, this came as an eye-opener to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because one reason, the reason it couldn't be found, most of the documents have been classified as secret and were not available until declassification took place of-- slowly over the years, the various documents have been declassified.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So it was after the declassification that took place that this colonel was able to find all of these records.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he has in here the complete report of all the testimony of all the witnesses in the case, which is over 100 pages long.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There's several pages in this, in this thing which he sent me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he has a complete report, the action of the higher headquarters.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And as I say, it came as an eye-opener to me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because I was never informed of any charges against anybody except General Patton said there were some serious charges.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But he didn't say what.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
